text.section:
In addition to any payment method authorized by law, and notwithstanding any statute to the contrary, any state agency may accept the following methods of payment to secure funds for deposit into the State Treasury:
Credit card;
Debit card;
Electronic check;
Automated clearinghouse (ACH) debit; or
Any other electronic payment method upon the prior written approval of both the Finance and Administration Cabinet and the Office of the State Treasurer.
